This is the area corresponding to the MI Sea. The second, third and fourth maps are inspired from [[Summer 2014 Event]] E-3 to E-5.<br>
'''There are no repair docks on this hexagon, it will be necessary to move to the adjacent ones to be able to repair ships.<br>'''
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 13#/V13-3|V13-3]] gives acces to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 13#/V13-4|V13-4]] ('''AL海域''').
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 13#/V13-4|V13-4]] gives acces to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 15#/V15-1|V15-1]] ('''深海棲地後方''').
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 6#/V6-4|V6-4]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 17#/V17-1|V17-1]] ('''深海棲地中枢部''').

